{"type": "article", "id": 8766, "title": "「 A’  设计大奖赛」之 Barb Perfume 石器香水", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-22T07:28:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235028mYgzwUKWfLEsJhCe.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这件作品出自俄罗斯艺术学院的学生之手，香水包装的灵感来源是远古石器时代的记忆，石头改变了人类的历史，同时蕴含着男性的原始力量，所以这款香水也是专门为男性设计。石头的包装内里嵌入了喷雾香水瓶，外面配有透明外盒，黑色的笔势狂放洒脱，男性气质十足。<a href=\"https://competition.adesignaward.com/design.php?ID=36959\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235026haetMLcSFKX6jAWP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235026FOu7dJVglRHbQapn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235027IKTBQMOLV1H649zw.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235027jhB0OqzSfNavEIRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.82777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}